{"tid":290353,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大阪京都6日5夜行程求狠評","createTime":"2017-06-19T16:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T10:48:50.000Z","uid":6878,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2107842da232b7428b518b88e75dd0087920768","tid":290353,"uid":6878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:57:41.000Z","msg":"黎緊下星期同朋友去6日大阪，好多野都唔識 求各位巴打幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1  <br />\n <br />\n16:00 關西機場落機 &gt; 買ICOCA &amp; HARUKA 去京都 &gt; 酒店放行李 &gt;拉麵小路&gt;京都塔<br />\n <br />\n住京都站附近<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 <br />\n<br />\n伏見稻荷 &gt; 袛園四條 &gt;花見小路&gt;八坂神社&gt;二三年坂&gt;清水寺<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n <br />\n酒店checkout &gt; 嵐山 &gt; 二條城 &gt; 返大阪 &gt; 梅田天神通+ 新梅田食道街 <br />\n<br />\n <br />\nDay 4 <br />\n <br />\n四天王寺 -&gt;天王寺動物園 -&gt; 梅田 &gt; 心齋橋, 道頓堀 <br />\n <br />\n呢日住動物園站附近 <br />\n<br />\nDay 5 <br />\n<br />\n(未諗到去邊，求建議，即日來回）住大阪 <br />\n <br />\nDay 6 <br />\n <br />\n黑門市場 &rarr; Rinku outlet &rarr; 關西機場 16:45 機<br />\n<br />\n交通方面如果ICOCA &amp; Haruka ＋ day 4 大阪周遊卡1day 係咪就ok <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外唔知買大阪周遊卡1day 抵唔抵玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大阪仲有咩景點推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907993e036a46cdbd8415f49fc1187da08f6d111","tid":290353,"uid":44677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:59:13.000Z","msg":"可以買2日osaka pass 我都save 返唔少 車錢"},{"pid":"360b9f940534dc23be34c4b1de62153ca745529e","tid":290353,"uid":6878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以買2日osaka pass 我都save 返唔少 車錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我應該暫時得一日係大阪市內玩 唔係應該買1日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dc3b14f7d6bc0a38c01e158bb705031e6b6a44","tid":290353,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"即日來回最例牌都係兩個選擇<br />\n奈良<br />\n神戶/姬路"},{"pid":"8248085651f2b691a680ae472544726f90e7dc59","tid":290353,"uid":92907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:08:35.000Z","msg":"離題<br />\n個動物園有隻被困到痴左線嘅熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51b9eb01942b7a9634818b1a8873fa2f6cad6e8","tid":290353,"uid":6878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即日來回最例牌都係兩個選擇<br />\n奈良<br />\n神戶/姬路</blockquote><br />\n因為個人唔太想去睇鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去神戶/姬路的話應該先去神戶市-&gt; 姬路城 定點？ <br />\n感謝巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420c1c6a82bfb7f0b61064a07c41496d3b18415e","tid":290353,"uid":6878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>離題<br />\n個動物園有隻被困到痴左線嘅熊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時去睇下佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b126f146018e55f26634a6c99ea586a469195425","tid":290353,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即日來回最例牌都係兩個選擇<br />\n奈良<br />\n神戶/姬路</blockquote><br />\n因為個人唔太想去睇鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去神戶/姬路的話應該先去神戶市-&gt; 姬路城 定點？ <br />\n感謝巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常都係去姬路城先<br />\n之後番神戶<br />\n可以睇埋夜景<br />\n<br />\n利申未去過"},{"pid":"4ae369259696b1a32c8028f45843f14be5aefe23","tid":290353,"uid":18641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T17:24:29.000Z","msg":"Day5 去飛田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f